title: LOWER SUGAR FRUIT ROCKETS
ingredients: Water, apple extract, apple juice from concentrate (7,9%), carrot juice from concentrate (3,9%), orange juice from concentrate (3,0%), raspberry puree (2,7%), spinach juice from concentrate (1,8%), beetroot juice from concentrate (1,3%), stabiliser: locust bean gum, acidity regulator: citric acid, natural flavourings, spirulina concentrate, safflower concentrate, orange extract, lemon juice concentrate. For allergens see ingredients in bold.

title: LOWER SUGAR MILK LOLLIES
ingredients: Reconstituted whole milk (78%), oligofructose, water, sugar, stabilisers (guar gum and carob gum), gelling agent (pectin), natural flavouring, vitamin D3.Reconstituted whole milk (73%), strawberry puree (10%), oligofructose, sugar, whole milk powder, stabilisers (guar gum and carob gum), gelling agent (pectin), beetroot juice concentrate, natural flavouring, vitamin D3.Reconstituted whole milk (74%), oligofructose, water, sugar, fat- reduced cocoa powder (1.2%), stabilisers (guar gum and carob gum), gelling agent (pectin), vitamin D3.

title: LOWER SUGAR WATERMELON ROCKETS
ingredients: Water, fructose, watermelon juice from concentrate (7.5%), concentrate (carrot, pumpkin, safflower, apple, lemon), stabiliser (locust bean gum), natural flavouring, acidity regulator (citric acid). May contain traces of allergens: milk, nuts and peanuts.
